<li class="g-item block-list-item">
<a id="block_1-0" class="comp block-small block" data-doc-id="1846837" href="https://www.lifewire.com/what-the-term-1080p-means-1846837" data-ordinal="6">
<div class="block-media"><img data-src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/PunizO8NraCn71i2m-UgjBC0zcc=/400x250/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(webp)/vizio-d-series-1080p-smart-tv-example-bb-cc-58b9e8dc5f9b58af5ccdcb72.jpg" src="https://:0/" alt="Vizio D-Series 1080p Smart TV Example" class="lazyload block-img js-justified" data-dim-ratio="1.515" data-expand="300"></div>
